* window.setTimeout
* window.setInterval
* window.requestAnimationFrame
* EventTarget.addEventListener
* EventTarget.removeEventListener
* XMLHTTPRequest.open
* XMLHTTPRequest.send
* window.fetch
* History.pushState
* History.replaceState

